Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\fad(1000,0)}註：夏威夷神話中的四位雪之女神之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自遙遠太空的未知生物 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們擁有人類所無法理解的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現在這個星球上已有40年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大半個世界都淪為了戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已進入戰鬥區域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60秒後降落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵循作戰計劃 迅速投身前線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都準備好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都是經過嚴格訓練篩選出的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你們一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到十分驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一號機 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二號機 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比報告上寫的還糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Second machine Olympia-Angels, landing check
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(640,655)}二號機 Olympia-Angels著陸確認
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要像哥哥這樣戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(685,655)\fs30}Billy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四號機 出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五號機 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六號機 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對Festum專用思維控制體感操縱式載人兵器法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1037,655)\fs30}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有被選中的人才能操縱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的底牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Type1 Type2 Type3 確認
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意Type4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內置敵人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其力量為人類所用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許我們早就滅亡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便還遠遠無法取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也用它爭取到了萌生希望的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛納基巡邏基地崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(518,655)}Mauna Kea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}註：夏威夷島上的五座火山之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部機能…都被敵人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊引導平民疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有部隊集結到北部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一防衛隊被殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距本島最終防衛線還有兩公里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(455,655)}Big Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃吧 那雷恩將軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(643,655)}Narain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是太平洋圈最大的運輸基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦這裡被攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數百萬人都會餓死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼都要守住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們學習了之前不屑一顧的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習了人類是如何自保的嗎 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能登機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們可都逼到眼前了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別急 馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛納基不會有事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總部發佈交戰規定α
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發佈對象為本島全域！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總部指揮的空襲部隊正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我接新聯合國總部！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的名義發佈攻擊中止令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有戰友在戰鬥啊！而且還有好幾萬平民！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交戰規定α必須遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剝奪沃爾特少校的職權 即刻逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,655)\fs30}Walter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雷恩將軍命令中止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸入坐標 進入攻擊態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 將軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都去搜尋生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我攻擊了友軍…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了…有人活著嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我們贏不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們 究竟是為了什麼 為了什麼而戰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曠日持久的戰爭讓世界凋敝不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能夠理解彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場戰爭是否也就能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣渺茫的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在世界的角落中等待破土
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是日本在戰亂中毀滅之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為傳承和平這一文化而建造的人工島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我曾經的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地區大賽就快到了 鼓起幹勁來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香明白 要老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香美香 你可別出全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近藤醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人受傷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續繼續…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到她就想起過去的一騎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去的…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 回去的時候上一騎那兒吃頓飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 你討厭我做的飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}堂馬廣登特別節目 追蹤神秘巨型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢廣登是做了多少節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹也是太有奉陪精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 無聊透頂 天氣還熱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我想去Alvis上班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別光學打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也得繼承島上的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好 里奈前輩…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事 鏑木？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你不是昨天就買過這本了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？那個…這本是收藏用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說鏑木 你是學生會長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道買漫畫 七夕祭典的準備都做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個…里奈前輩不在討論就沒法進行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夠不爭氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然下次到一騎前輩那裡一起討論？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 里奈前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之後有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我在上班啊 怎麼可能會有空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也…是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ改 上臂引擎安裝完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請進行FTP試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連接確認完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越來越熟練了呢 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(788,655)\fs30}Kanon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了媽媽的教導
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡可是職員兼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 羽佐間老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 出去吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天待在這兒要悶出病來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是想去一騎那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒無所謂…去哪裡都成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不希望再有人駕駛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又要把它組裝起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到卡農會去學工程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小年紀技術卻很了得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是想做你徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乾脆退休算了 畢竟還得畫這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真的是駕駛員培養教材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊 西尾老師開口的事沒法推託啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該吃飯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就老規矩 去吃咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎 會趕不上午市的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有問題的 讓我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是御門的 東西我搬到裡面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 老爸教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說這個 一騎哥 有客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 你來得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午的研究收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子準備還沒好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我過會兒再來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧 吃飯是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是暉咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 新品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是 不過菜名加上廚師的名字是這裡的規矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如一騎咖喱什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是溝口先生擅自加的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很尊敬一騎前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也不會輸給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見和溝口先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾天一直都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虧我還以為能和遠見前輩一起工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows呼叫控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已捕捉到不明機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}unknown follow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸入自動瞄準程式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這招怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖定目標 發射飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}Target Fox-One
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你超前了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}run out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能因為自己飛得快就把敵人給超了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 坐在大飛機上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽她啊 最近總是這樣淨跟幻想中的朋友說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因為沒有同齡的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得不用太擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很感性 所以我就是放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真矢姐姐也坐在飛機上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了呢 艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,655)\fs30}Emery
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農是蜜瓜雪頂和…請用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼啊 我可沒點這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免費贈送
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你常常來光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個你喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是不…討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見學航空 卡農學工科 劍司學醫療 要投身教育
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都決定了各自的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士你搞研究嗎 感覺挺合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？在咖啡館當廚師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 還挺合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想讓當年的王牌駕駛員的寶貴經驗發揮餘熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當教官也是個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些痕跡 不開法芙娜了也還是留著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是尼伯龍根連接導致的小規模同化現象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(433,655)\fs30}Nibelungen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會找到治療方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始學些什麼 做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後這些事卻以未完成收場 我不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是這樣的嗎 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有希望恢復的 別太悲觀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有三年…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼長的時間 足夠我做心理準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何況現在眼睛也能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是和平安穩的 重要的夥伴生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我會一直在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你一直保護著這個島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 怎麼了 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對什麼東西起反應了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫CDC 不明機體接近
