Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一個十分美麗的島上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 艾梅莉好像也感應到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想讓我們見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫CDC 緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows 維持距離跟上
